<br>
Airpet with BO5 and DS is about an even match, but a single nuke or heal puts it on top. After the first few I stopped bothering with gearing up and healing and just nuked a bit more. Took 2 mobs down with 1 pet then cannibalized back to full and started on the next 2. Does not seem efficient, but it works for me. Get a partner shammie / cleric and you can roll <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
